cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CC, cs.NE 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and semantics. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses logistic regression for training. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with learning the semantics of transitive verbs. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the complexity of disambiguation tasks. 
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also less likely but possible as the paper deals with the use of vectors and matrices in representing semantics.
